# Vincent — data & providers

## State & persistence

- **`Cellar.kt`** — in-memory SSOT (Compose snapshot state); all UI reads/writes here.
- **`CellarRepository`** (common) → **`RoomCellarRepository`** (android) over `VincentDatabase`.
- Entities/DAOs in `androidMain/.../db/` (`BottleEntity`, `BottleDao`, migrations in `VincentDatabase.kt`).
- Enums stored by name — no TypeConverter.

## Wine lookup (`ProductLookup.kt`)

Providers implement `WineDataProvider`. Order set in `ProductLookup.android.kt` → `wineDataProviders()`:

1. Open Food Facts (`BARCODE_SCAN`) — no key
2. grapeminds (`TEXT_SEARCH`, `LABEL_SCAN`, `ENRICH`) — `GRAPEMINDS_API_KEY`
3. CellarTracker (`TEXT_SEARCH`, `PRICE`) — stub, returns empty
4. AI Label / Gemini (`LABEL_SCAN`) — `AI_PROXY_URL` (prod) or `GEMINI_API_KEY` (debug)

Routing: barcode → first non-null; text search → merge results. `WineDataSource.enrich()` fills rich fields from grapeminds.

## AI (`ai/`)

| Module | Role |
|--------|------|
| `WineAi.kt` | `WineRecognizer`, `PriceEstimator`, `FoodPairer` |
| `WineAi.android.kt` | Gemini Flash HTTP client |
| `Dictation.kt` | Voice → transcript → AI fill |
| `PhotoCapture.kt` | Camera → label recognition |
| `Barcode.kt` | ML Kit code scanner |

## Other data modules

- **Auth** — `Auth.kt` + `GoogleSignIn.android.kt`, Firebase Auth
- **CloudSync** — Firestore `users/{uid}/…`, last-write-wins
- **CsvFormat** — import/export (Vincent / Vivino / PLOC tolerant mapping)
- **FileTransfer** — Storage Access Framework (expect/actual)

## Adding a provider

1. Implement `WineDataProvider` in `ProductLookup.android.kt`
2. Register in `wineDataProviders()` at the correct priority
3. Add config key to `composeApp/build.gradle.kts` `secret()` if needed
4. Document in `README.md` provider table
